description:
The Jester ranked 8th takes on The Assassin ranked
10th in this sanctioned US match. It is a close match
throughout all three rounds, with both wrestlers
gaining control and style and both desperately vying
for the victory. Which wrester won by 4pts? Which
wrestler got fucked like a loser on the mat in RD4?
Watch to find out...
title: The Jester (2-6) Ranked 8th
